@startuml
actor "Logistic Operator" as Operator
participant "Qualification Management System" as System

Operator -> System: Request to create new Qualification\n(provides Code, Name)
activate System

System -> System: Validate provided Code and Name
alt Code is unique and data valid
    System -> System: Save new Qualification to database
    System --> Operator: Success confirmation
else Validation fails
    System --> Operator: Error message (duplicate code or invalid data)
end

Operator -> System: Request to update existing Qualification\n(provides Code, Name)
activate System

System -> System: Validate updated data and existence
alt Data valid and Qualification exists
    System -> System: Update Qualification in database
    System --> Operator: Success confirmation
else Validation fails or not exists
    System --> Operator: Error message (not found or invalid input)
end

Operator -> System: Request list of Qualifications (with filters)
activate System

System -> System: Query database with filters
System --> Operator: List of Qualifications (filtered by Code/Name)

deactivate System
@enduml
